article_title: First came the alert message, then the boom of interceptions
sentence: The  Palestinian  civil  defence  authority  in  the  occupied  West  Bank  city  of  Jericho  said  a  man  there  died  during  the  Iranian  missile  barrage.

article_title: First came the alert message, then the boom of interceptions
sentence: According  to  the  AFP  news  agency,  which  spoke  to  city  governor  Hussein  Hamayel,  the  victim  was  killed  by  falling  rocket  debris.
